title: 'Franz Ferdinand': outlined sans caps with low F-bar
content:
Does anybody know what font was used for their new logo?

[http://www.franzferdinand.co.uk/images/globals/logo.png](http://web.archive.org/web/20100202015648/http:/www.franzferdinand.co.uk/images/globals/logo.png "http://www.franzferdinand.co.uk/images/globals/logo.png")

author: jim_

comments.content: Not likely. Tungsten was released six months _after_ this was posted on Typophile. Not that I know what it is, but those F's look modified.
